NAME
    WWW::RIPE::LIRPortal - Automated access to the RIPE NCC LIRPortal

SYNOPSIS
      use WWW::RIPE::LIRPortal;

      my $w = WWW::RIPE::LIRPortal->new;

      $w->login( regid    => 'xx.joes',
                 username => 'joe',
                 password => 'secret' );

      print $w->regxml(version => '0.1');

DESCRIPTION
    WWW::RIPE::LIRPortal provides a simple OO interface to logging in and
    retrieving registry information from the RIPE NCC LIRPortal.

METHODS
    new()
        Creates a new WWW::RIPE::LIRPortal object

    login()
        Logs into the LIR Portal.

        Arguments: regid => $regid, username => $username, password =>
        $password

    regxml(version => $version)
        Returns registry data as XML.

BUGS
    Please report bugs, patches or feature requests to <swbugs@ripe.net>

